aria (0.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * v0.2.2 release
  * GUI toolkit wrappers (GTK4, SDL2, raylib)
  * 9 new ecosystem libraries (172/172 tests passing)
  * LSP improvements: documentSymbol, references, signatureHelp
  * MCP improvements: aria_format tool, structured errors, resources
  * aria_make: test runner command
  * Debugger: conditional breakpoints, logpoints, exception filters
  * Safety audit: 4 new checks (unsafe, extern, cast, TODO), JSON output
  * Specialist model v5

